<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Slight' Tremor Felt in Istanbul 21 Apr </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2104185594 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 21 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2104185594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over still of regional map] </F>
  [Text] A slight tremor was felt in Istanbul in the 
afternoon. There was no loss of life or damage to property. 
According to the information received from the Bogazici 
University Kandilli Observatory Directorate, the epicenter of 
the tremor was around Beykoz. It occurred at 1640 [1340 GMT] 
and registered 3.0 on the Richter scale. 

