<H3> <TI>   Poll Shows Balladur Losing Popularity </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Poll Shows Balladur Losing Popularity </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1904142494 Paris PARIS MATCH in French 21 Apr 94 pp 
86-87--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR1904142494 </F>
