Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2204173194 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>
<F P=105>  Swedish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Svea court of appeal today lowered the sentence 
of a 29-year-old woman who has been spying on Iranian refugees 
in Sweden for the Iranian Intelligence Service. The city court 
sentenced the woman to 18 months imprisonment for spying, but 
the court of appeal lowered the sentence to nine months. 

