<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Turkish Prime Minister Tansu Ciller has denied 
rumors that she made concessions in connection with the Cyprus 
issue. Discussing the details of her conversation with President 
Clinton on the Cyprus issue in Turkish newspapers today, Ciller 
