<H3> <TI>   Meets With Ministers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Meets With Ministers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2504190294 Warsaw PAP in English 1823 GMT 25 Apr 94--FOR 
