<AU>   FBIS-WEU-94-080 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  26 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> UNITED KINGDOM </F>
<H3> <TI>   Jordan's King Husayn Meets U.S Secretary of State </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Jordan's King Husayn Meets U.S Secretary of State </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WA2604114694 </F>
<F P=103> WA2604114694 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
BFN 

    For reportage on the meeting between King Husayn of Jordan 
and U.S. Secretary of State Warren Christopher in London on 25 
April and the text of the proceedings of the joint news 
conference by King Husayn and Secretary Christopher, see the 
Jordan section of the 26 April issue of the NEAR EAST &amp; SOUTH 
ASIA Daily Report. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

